dc_description_s: This data layer represents addresses for Portage County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Portage_Addresses_2018.gdb'. [Site address points represent the location of site or service delivery addresses assigned by local governments.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://www.co.portage.wi.gov/375/Land-Information-GIS
